message.content:
1. FMD increased by 0.73% after maraviroc intensification.
2. The interquartile range (IQR) of the FMD increase after maraviroc intensification was -0.25 to 1.70.
3. FMD decreased by -0.42% in the control period.
4. The interquartile range (IQR) of the FMD decrease in the control period was -1.89 to 0.25.
5. The difference in FMD changes between the maraviroc intensification and the control period was statistically significant with a p-value of 0.049.
